title: Homeworld Soundtrack
description:
This is the soundtrack to the computer game "Homeworld". All songs have been ripped to 256 kbps (CBR) MP3 files. I think this is a beautiful score, so enjoy it!

The files in this torrent come from a rip of the official soundtrack CD that shipped with the "Game of the Year Edition", so the sound quality is a lot higher compared to that of the files extracted from the game itself.
